data.description: Nestled in the Meridian neighborhood of the desired Riverpark community along the scenic walking path. This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom residence spans an impressive 2,062 square feet and boasts one of the most coveted floor plans. The heart of this home is its generously sized island kitchen outfitted with brand-new counters and stainless appliances. The first floor offers expansive living area, complete with a cozy fireplace and tile flooring. Convenient first level bedroom and a full bathroom. Outdoor living space with inviting paver stone patio. Second floor, you'll discover the spacious primary suite, featuring a walk-in closet, walk-in shower and a relaxing jacuzzi tub. Three additional bedrooms, and full bath along with an upstairs laundry room for your added convenience. Nestled in the Meridian neighborhood of the desired Riverpark community along the scenic walking path. This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom residence spans an impressive 2,062 square feet and boasts one of the most coveted floor plans. The heart of this home is its generously sized island kitchen outfitted with brand-new counters and stainless appliances. The first floor offers expansive living area, complete with a cozy fireplace and tile flooring. Convenient first level bedroom and a full bathroom. Outdoor living space with inviting paver stone patio. Second floor, you'll discover the spacious primary suite, featuring a walk-in closet, walk-in shower and a relaxing jacuzzi tub. Three additional bedrooms, and full bath along with an upstairs laundry room for your added convenience. Central AC to keep you comfortable on warm days. A spacious attached two-car garage and a driveway provide ample parking options. The Riverpark community offers a wealth of amenities, including proximity to schools, scenic walking trails, multiple parks and more. Moments to all The Collection and new Wagon Wheel developments have to offer. Easy access to the 101 freeway, welcome to your new beginning!
